      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">52.209-2</ph> Prohibition on Contracting
with Inverted Domestic Corporations-Representation.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="provision" class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d3127e8" class="- topic/p ">As prescribed
in <ph class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="FAR-i1116431.dita#i1116431"
                     base="i1116431"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">9.108-5</xref>(a)</ph>, insert
the following provision:</p>
         <p outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" class="- topic/p ">Prohibition on Contracting with Inverted
Domestic Corporations-Representation <ph outputclass = "SmCaps">(Nov 2015)</ph></p>
         <ol id="d3089e25" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3127e19" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Definitions</i>.
“Inverted domestic corporation” and “subsidiary” have the meaning
given in the clause of this contract entitled Prohibition on Contracting
with Inverted Domestic Corporations (<xref href="FAR-i1062680.dita#i1062680"
                        base="i1062680"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.209-10</xref>).</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3127e29" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> Government
agencies are not permitted to use appropriated (or otherwise made
available) funds for contracts with either an inverted domestic
corporation, or a subsidiary of an inverted domestic corporation,
unless the exception at <xref href="FAR-i1116407.dita#i1116407"
                        base="i1116407"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">9.108-2</xref>(b)
applies or the requirement is waived in accordance with the procedures
at <xref href="FAR-i1116422.dita#i1116422"
                        base="i1116422"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">9.108-4</xref>.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d3127e40" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Representation</i>.
The Offeror represents that-</p>
               <ol id="d3089e68" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3127e48" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph> It <cite outputclass="Checkbox" xtrc="52.209-2_d49e52">□</cite> is, <cite outputclass="Checkbox" xtrc="52.209-2_d49e55">□</cite> is
not an inverted domestic corporation; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d3127e53" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph> It <cite outputclass="Checkbox" xtrc="52.209-2_d49e63">□</cite> is, <cite outputclass="Checkbox" xtrc="52.209-2_d49e66">□</cite> is
not a subsidiary of an inverted domestic corporation.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
         <p outputclass="Endofprovision" class="- topic/p ">(End of provision)</p>
